    <item>
      <title>CVS 因医疗成本上涨下调年度利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/cvs-cuts-annual-profit-outlook-citing-rising-medical-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CVS Health Corp. 因医疗保险业务的医疗成本增加而连续下调第二季度的年度盈利预期，该公司股价在盘前交易中大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/cvs-cuts-annual-profit-outlook-citing-rising-medical-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行出租竞争对手的资产负债表以规避资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/rent-the-balance-sheet-banks-seek-ways-to-skirt-capital-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，巴克莱银行一直在纠结如何处理其美国信用卡业务。它是一个现金发生器，产生稳定的收入流，但由于监管机构迫使银行留出资本作为损失缓冲，其运营成本高昂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/rent-the-balance-sheet-banks-seek-ways-to-skirt-capital-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其提高里拉存款利息税以削减预算赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/turkey-raises-tax-on-lira-deposit-interest-to-cut-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其提高了里拉储蓄利息收入的税率，以增加政府收入并帮助缩小不断扩大的预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/turkey-raises-tax-on-lira-deposit-interest-to-cut-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 10:28:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜日落酒店集团拟寻求 3 亿美元扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/dubai-s-sunset-hospitality-said-to-seek-300-million-to-expand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜的 Sunset Hospitality Group 旗下拥有 Sushisamba 连锁餐厅和豪华 METT Hotels &amp; 等品牌。据知情人士透露，Resorts 正在寻求筹集约 3 亿美元用于扩张计划。]]></description>
